						<div class="postbody">I can assure you that creating a new PPU will be a much bigger problem that whatever you are currently facing with the SNES. If the NES PPU isn't enough for you, just don't use the NES, get over whatever problem you have with other platforms and use those.
<br />
<br />Even if by a miracle you were able to "upgrade" the NES PPU, what would be the point if you were the only one with such an upgraded console? Nobody would be able to play your game(s). On the other hand, lots of people have perfectly good SNESs.</div>

